Package: orgcharter
Title: Make data-driven organisation charts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tom", "Smith", , "tomsmith_uk@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Use a spreadsheet of organisation to build publication-ready 
  organisation charts.  Clarify and communicate your organisation's structure to
  everyone who needs to know.  Easily filter the datasource to produce charts of
  smaller organisation areas (divisions, departments, or projects).
